  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK734">
<l>uṟupaciyu mōvāp piṇiyuñ ceṟupakaiyuñ</l>
<l>cērā tiyalvatu nāṭu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>A kingdom is that which continues to be free from excessive starvation, irremediable epidemics, and destructive foes.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
